body:
@szpak Your intuition is correct.  I am using Spring Boot version `2.0.5.RELEASE`, and it is using an older version of the Mockito library.  In order to use the newest Mockito, I had to change my Gradle config:
```
    testCompile('org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-test') {
        exclude group: "org.mockito", module: "mockito-core"
    }
    testCompile("org.mockito:mockito-core:2.23.4")
```

That fixed my errors.  Thank you for the help.

> testCompile('org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-test') {
>         exclude group: "org.mockito", module: "mockito-core"
>     }
>     testCompile("org.mockito:mockito-core:2.23.4")

this works like a charm, Thank You!
